(crying, sniffling,
kissing)

17:38.752 --> 17:40.651
Um, are...
are you okay?

17:40.653 --> 17:43.955
I think... think maybe seeing
your ex was a bit much for you.

17:43.957 --> 17:46.174
No. Not at all.

17:46.176 --> 17:48.176
I want... only you.

17:48.178 --> 17:49.927
Oh, yeah.

17:49.929 --> 17:53.097
I want to...
I want to rock your world.

17:53.099 --> 17:55.433
And you're so hot.
(sniffling)

17:55.435 --> 17:59.137
I want to ride you
like a bronco.

17:59.139 --> 18:01.422
(sobbing)
Okay, Cassie. Cassie.

18:01.424 --> 18:03.507
Yeah, we...
we can't do this.

18:03.509 --> 18:04.809
I mean, you're crying.

18:04.811 --> 18:06.060
(coughing)

18:06.062 --> 18:07.445
And contagious.

18:07.447 --> 18:08.780
You're-you're having

18:08.782 --> 18:10.148
a really, really bad week.

18:10.150 --> 18:12.150
I think... I think
you should just

18:12.152 --> 18:14.752
take it easy.

18:14.754 --> 18:15.870
You're right.

18:15.872 --> 18:18.373
I'm not in a good place.
No.

18:18.375 --> 18:19.457
Oh, wow.

18:19.459 --> 18:21.459
I probably would have
let you do

18:21.461 --> 18:24.195
all sorts of crazy things to me.

18:24.197 --> 18:26.381
(sighs)

18:27.549 --> 18:29.300
Exactly.

18:29.302 --> 18:31.335
I release you.

18:31.337 --> 18:33.638
Go have fun this weekend.

18:33.640 --> 18:35.223
Meet someone else.

18:35.225 --> 18:37.058
TED: <i>Yes! Yes! Be cool.</i>
Okay.

18:37.060 --> 18:39.060
NARRATOR: <i>But I couldn't</i>
<i>meet someone else.</i>

18:39.062 --> 18:41.062
Hey, Ted?
Yeah.

18:41.064 --> 18:42.213
Everyone here is saying

18:42.215 --> 18:44.515
you and Cassie are the
couple of the weekend.

18:44.517 --> 18:45.850
How great is that?

18:45.852 --> 18:47.735
NARRATOR:
<i>Barney was right.</i>

18:47.737 --> 18:50.605
<i>I'd chosen poorly,</i>
<i>everyone had seen us together,</i>

18:50.607 --> 18:52.723
<i>and now the whole weekend</i>
<i>seemed lost.</i>

18:52.725 --> 18:55.159
<i>Until...</i>

18:55.161 --> 18:57.561
Hi. I just got here.

18:57.563 --> 18:59.447
Did I miss anything?

18:59.449 --> 19:02.417
Not at all. Grace, right?

19:02.419 --> 19:05.620
I'm Ted. Let's get you a drink
before you talk to anyone else

19:05.622 --> 19:07.839
or hear anything.

19:09.174 --> 19:10.858
Hey, guys.
How's your night going?

19:10.860 --> 19:12.176
Ugh!
Ugh!

19:12.178 --> 19:13.928
Our minister just died.

19:13.930 --> 19:15.913
Wh...?
We can still use the church,

19:15.915 --> 19:17.765
but we only have two days
to find a new officiant.

19:17.767 --> 19:19.133
Unless...

19:19.243 --> 19:20.334
BARNEY:
Wedding at Bernie's!

19:20.335 --> 19:21.835
We're not doing
Wedding at Bernie's!

19:21.837 --> 19:24.754
Wow. Oh, that's terrible.

19:24.756 --> 19:26.723
Should I make a toast
in his honor?

19:26.725 --> 19:28.308
(whispers):
No.

19:28.310 --> 19:29.726
Of course I should.

19:30.678 --> 19:32.128
Everyone?

19:32.130 --> 19:33.763
To Reverend Lowell.

19:33.765 --> 19:35.732
He may have
passed away

19:35.734 --> 19:37.133
tonight, but
he will always...

19:37.135 --> 19:39.169
Uncle Robert died?!

19:39.987 --> 19:41.571
Oh, no.

19:41.573 --> 19:43.907
(crying)

19:46.878 --> 19:48.811
(high-pitched crying)

19:48.813 --> 19:50.030
(sobbing)

19:50.032 --> 19:51.832
Have a nice weekend.

19:51.834 --> 19:54.784
NARRATOR: <i>All that night, I did nothing</i>
<i>but choose poorly.</i>

19:54.786 --> 19:56.169
<i>But thanks to Cassie,</i>

19:56.171 --> 19:58.722
<i>I didn't get together</i>
<i>with anyone at that wedding.</i>

19:58.724 --> 20:00.040
<i>And if I had,</i>

20:00.042 --> 20:04.127
<i>well, then, your mother</i>
<i>and I might never have met.</i>

20:04.129 --> 20:07.997
<i>So, maybe, in a way,</i>
<i>I chose wisely.</i>

20:08.712 --> 20:11.692
SOPHIA:
Boo-uh! Boo-uh! Eee!

20:11.693 --> 20:13.526
<i>Although, it sure as heck</i>

20:13.528 --> 20:14.745
<i>didn't feel like it</i>
<i>at the time.</i>

20:14.746 --> 20:16.029
Aah! Aah! Aah!

20:16.031 --> 20:17.664
(sighs)

20:17.666 --> 20:19.532
She chose...

20:19.534 --> 20:20.917
Wesley.

20:20.919 --> 20:22.285
(chuckling)

20:22.287 --> 20:24.838
I've been dying
to say that one all night.

20:26.657 --> 20:28.625
Look, I'm sorry
I yelled at you.

20:28.627 --> 20:29.992
The truth is, you're right.

20:29.994 --> 20:32.829
It was wrong of me to take
that job without telling Lily.

20:32.831 --> 20:35.799
I don't need to be tough
with her. I need to be fair.

20:35.801 --> 20:37.434
Thanks, Marshall.
Mm.

20:37.436 --> 20:39.552
I should also apologize.

20:39.554 --> 20:41.771
While you were filling the tank,

20:41.773 --> 20:44.357
I may have been so angry,

20:44.359 --> 20:47.544
I texted your wife with the news

20:47.546 --> 20:50.213
that you took that judge offer.

20:50.215 --> 20:52.032
(phone ringing)

20:52.034 --> 20:53.950
Don't forget
to compliment her hair.

